title: Practice

A test will follow.

press ENTER to begin.

content:
These were the practice trials.

Great! Let's go on and do the actual test.

In this test, you will learn to recognize six cars.

To begin memorizing the first car, press ENTER.

trialText: Review the cars (20 seconds)

content:
Now your memory of these cars will be tested.

In the remaining trials, the correct answer can be any of the six cars.

The incorrect cars are sometimes very similar to the target cars, so be sure to look at each car prior to answering.

press ENTER.
